  "detailed_description": "<h1>Find hidden objects with Millie!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/25ba62f4e0810c1473d86da690d97572.avif?t=1772361359\" width=600 height=190 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Help Millie and her friends uncover hidden objects in this cozy adventure! Explore family-friendly puzzles in playful locations from Millie's bedroom to her classroom, and have fun learning along the way!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361359\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/927be8cd10429359d5ca2c41b01adbeb.poster.avif?t=1772361359\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/927be8cd10429359d5ca2c41b01adbeb.webm?t=1772361359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/927be8cd10429359d5ca2c41b01adbeb.mp4?t=1772361359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361359\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Millie and Friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Millie and her friends on a cozy adventure to find hidden objects in charming, family-friendly environments. Explore scenes like bedrooms and holiday settings, offering a relaxing puzzle experience perfect for all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361359\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/f573ad29483fd808a96e1e948bd097a1.poster.avif?t=1772361359\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/f573ad29483fd808a96e1e948bd097a1.webm?t=1772361359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/f573ad29483fd808a96e1e948bd097a1.mp4?t=1772361359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346300/extras/9c7eaccfa41c3097c13017e52b12308e.webp?t=1772361359\" width=584 height=41 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With beautifully crafted environments, including schools, Halloween scenes, and Christmas settings, the game invites you to solve puzzles at your own pace. Helpful tips ensure a fun and accessible experience, making it a wholesome and relaxing game for everyone.</p>",
